data.description: "Step into modern elegance with this remarkable 4 bed, 2 bath home situated on an oversized corner lot in a newly established neighborhood, mere moments away from convenient interstate access on US 67. Boasting a mere year of age, this new construction home exudes contemporary charm at every turn.  As you enter, a sense of tranquility envelopes you, with the master bedroom thoughtfully secluded on one side for ultimate privacy and relaxation. The remaining three bedrooms on the opposite end provide ample space for both family and guests, ensuring comfort for all.  The heart of the home shines with an open concept design, seamlessly integrating the living room, kitchen, and dining areas. Ideal for hosting gatherings or simply enjoying everyday life, this layout offers a perfect blend of functionality and style.  Don't miss this unparalleled opportunity to own a piece of luxury living in a prime location that delivers both convenience and comfort. Make this stunning property yours and elevate your lifestyle today!"
